Usability Specialist Recruitment
Title: User Interface Usability Specialist
Position: Full-Time Regular
Location: Beijing, China
Education: Bachelor\'s Degree in Human Computer Interaction, Cognitive Psychology, Industrial Design, Graphical design or equivalent
Description: 
Profile
This position is ideal for those who enjoy problem solving. Fresh thinking is a must, as well as excellent communication skills.
Description
The Usability Specialist works closely with the UFIDA development community. The Usability Specialist is responsible for the ensuring that software products meet user requirements. The Usability Specialist is also responsible for the creation and delivery of design patterns, samples, design guidelines and design best practices. 
Key Responsibilities
oCreation of guidelines for interaction design
oSupervision of the guidelines Implementation
oConduction of user testing and heuristic evaluation
oDevelopment of prototypes for new products
oHold Focus groups, interview, think aloud, and so on.
Experience: 
o 1 years experience in usability engineering or HCI field is a plus.
Skills:
oTechnical Writing
oUsability methods, such as field observation and cognitive walkthrough
oExperimental Deign, conduct and data analysis
Motivated candidates please send you resume to this email address: yaz@ufsoft.com.cn and cc to whr@ufsoft.com.cn
 
